{"tid":673560,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"同方力申過「520」莊思敏落閘：冇諗過發展！","createTime":"2018-05-22T03:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T13:45:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0061344d4624fda3b6bb243a28660be7528228","tid":673560,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"藝人莊思敏、周文健及陸詩韻等昨晚出席娛樂公司晚宴，問到與方力申共度「520」，並在社交網上載合照「放閃」，莊思敏說：「其實係因為聽日佛誕，我哋成日去寺廟做義工，咁啱撞到啫！我覺得參與慈善工作，唔需要刻意約埋一齊。（有發展機會？）冇諗過，我哋亦冇討論過呢件事。（接受到矮過自己嘅男仔？）都得嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n至於周文健早前客串了一部電影：「呢排休息，遲啲去俄羅斯睇世界盃。（全男班？）太太都去，但佢唔睇波嘅。」陸詩韻則忙於拍古裝電影：「好熱，捱夜好辛苦，唔明點解夏天要拍古裝，不過暫時都仲Handle到！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FtA20IOZEzrSdK2HeMsdDA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/da0c35264b770540e811db072673565b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFtA20IOZEzrSdK2HeMsdDA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fda0c35264b770540e811db072673565b&h=3d12bdb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Z8EjT5s1SJFgcizIn3qlDQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/2d0b18d26275e54c29ac3ea77508506b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZ8EjT5s1SJFgcizIn3qlDQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F2d0b18d26275e54c29ac3ea77508506b&h=5da6dc85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%90%8C%E6%96%B9%E5%8A%9B%E7%94%B3%E9%81%8E-520-%E8%8E%8A%E6%80%9D%E6%95%8F%E8%90%BD%E9%96%98-%E5%86%87%E8%AB%97%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95-214500530.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2596%25B9%